ATTRIBUTION
============================================================================

The `engine.py` module is a reconstruction of Thomas Dybdahl Ahle's Sunfish
chess engine (https://github.com/thomasahle/sunfish), which is itself
distributed under the GPL. This project inherits the GPL-3.0-or-later license
on that basis.

